  "Analysis_Intersection": "Step-by-step reasoning of whether the road's actual physical surface touches or crosses the parcel boundary line.",
  "RoadAvailable": "Yes", "No", or "ERROR" (Use ERROR only if the lot itself could not be identified)
}
